text: Jean Omer Beriziky (born 9 September 1950"Omer Beriziky, le Premier Ministre de consensus de la Transition" , Tana News, 29 October 2011 .) is a Malagasy politician and diplomat. He was the Prime Minister of Madagascar from 2011 to 2014.
